NAME

DateTime::Locale::kw - Locale data examples for the Cornish (kw) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Cornish locale.

  dy Meurth
  dy Merher
  dy Yow
  dy Gwener
  dy Sadorn
  dy Sul

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 mis Hwevrer 5, dy Meurth
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 mis Kevardhu 22, dy Gwener
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 mis Gwynngala 15, dy Sadorn

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 mis Hwevrer 5
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 mis Kevardhu 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 mis Gwynngala 15

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 Hwe 5
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 Kev 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 Gwn 15

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008-02-05
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995-12-22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10-09-15

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04:44:23 UTC

Available Formats

Bh (h B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 B

Bhm (h:mm B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6:30 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44 B

Bhms (h:mm:ss B)

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05:02 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44:23 B

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Gwe
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Sad

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Gwe 9:05 a.m.
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Sad 4:44 a.m.

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Sad 4:44:23 a.m.
